metadata.name: JADED-TIVATION
metadata.description:
This one's for every creative who have felt disconnected from who they are, the ones that battle with themselves, who lack motivation yet still find a way to create beauty from the chaos and for those who are yet to come out of the void.

This is a reminder that it's not uncreative but self loving to take a break from the chaos and concurrently, never stop believing in the artist that you are.  
You are gold.  
You are a treasure.  
You are relevant.  
And that alone tops it all.
